Class ReferencePhoto

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models.attachments.ReferencePhoto

    public class ReferencePhoto
extends java.lang.Object

    Model for storing information related to a reference photo. Includes the uuid of the photo, and a bodypart + label to identify the photo.
